_sText:
June 16, 2014 // Baghdad, Iraq

In-response to the Iraqi Government's support of the American-led intervention in the Middle-East, the LEET CREW Initiates an attack on the newly rebuilt Ministry of Defense building in Baghdad, Holding 3 US Officials Hostage.

A team of SEAL TEAM 6 Operatos arrive at the scene just 20 Minutes after the incident was reported all over the local media.


cs_ministry is a Hostage Rescue map based off of PowerThrust's Layout from cs_officerescue.
The map has been in development for a good month and just reached its first Beta stage.

As of now, expect fast gunfights and rotations from BOTs. Offline team balance will be based on how good you play and coordinate CPU Players. This version was NOT tested In PVP.

Current Features:
  • HDR
  • Basic Bot Support
  • 16 Players Support

To Be Added:
  • Built Cubemaps
  • Custom Soundscapes
  • Radar/Overview
  • Extended Pathways
  • More detail

Note:
The map has not been finalized. Feedback and Suggestions are welcome!
